  "Description": {
    "English": "This small extension to the ship's automated defense network appears to be its own autonomous organism. A small mouth in the centre of its flesh hungers for <span class=\"name name-special\">Pugneum</span>.<br><br>During combat, it seems to hijack the neurological array and prevent fear or pain from traumatising the rest of the ship's body.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "该舰自动化防御网络的这一小部分延伸似乎是它自己的自主有机体。它的中央有一个小嘴巴渴望吞食<span class=\"name name-special\">普茵</span>。<br><br>在战斗中，它似乎劫持了神经系统阵列，防止恐惧或疼痛对船上其他部位造成创伤。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這是太空船自動防禦系統的小型配件，彷彿像是獨立存在的生物。位於肉體中心的小型口腔渴望<span class=\"name name-special\">搏</span>。<br><br>戰鬥時，尖叫抑制器會控制神經陣列，避免恐懼或疼痛對太空船的其他部位造成創傷。"
  },
